stickerText: Do you prefer matcha or coffee? I personally don’t understand people who can’t be vulnerable with their loved ones. How are they supposed to know what we’re thinking if we don’t tell them what we want? How can they do the bare minimum when they don’t even know what that is? Or do we blame them for not knowing when it’s really just our ego stopping us from telling them bc we don’t want to seem weak? I like coffee in the morning and matcha for lunch, but both always with collagen.
